General.Name: Lovisa Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Lovisa Holdings Limited engages in the retail sale of fashion jewelry and accessories. It designs, develops, sources, and merchandises fashion jewelry and accessories under the Lovisa brand name. It operated its stores in Australia, New Zealand, Singapore, Malaysia, South Africa, the United Kingdom, France, Luxembourg, Belgium, Germany, the Netherlands, Austria, Switzerland, the United States, Poland, Canada, Spain, and the Middle East. Lovisa Holdings Limited was founded in 2010 and is based in Hawthorn, Australia.
